meanings: a wasteland of nauseating 'issue-based' teen dramas such as "Moesha", "South of Nowhere", "Miracle's Boys", and worst of all "Degrassi" (with the exception of "Radio Free Roscoe", one of the few escapist teen shows out there but also the BEST!)
Nightime on the kids network Noggin, which also happens to be a division of Nickelodeon, which also happens to be a shitty kids network. The-N is a great channel along with Fuse and HBO.
television channel containing teenage shows such as Degrassi:The Next Generation, Instant Star and Girls vs. Boys. They used to show Pete and Pete but it got cancelled.
